{"tid":6875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄邊界在哪裏？ 普京：俄羅斯疆域無限!!!!!!","createTime":"2016-11-27T14:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T16:50:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"492c4a1af108a3514c1fd5f43134008c450e8d0e","tid":6875,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161125/large/1480036245_0572.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161125%2Flarge%2F1480036245_0572.jpg&h=0949eb5a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(互聯網) <br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京周四出席俄羅斯地理學會頒獎禮時，說笑地告訴一位學生「俄羅斯疆域無限」，卻可能令很多人心寒。 <br />\n<br />\n在那個在電視播出的頒獎禮上，普京問自稱各國邊界無所不曉的9歲神童，清不清楚俄羅斯邊界在哪裏，神童答：「俄羅斯邊界止於白令海峽，與美國相望。」普京抱抱神童，糾正他，說：「俄羅斯疆域是無限的。」但他隨即補一句：「說笑罷了！」身兼俄羅斯地理學會會長的國防部長肖古（Sergei Shoigu）也笑起來。 <br />\n可能知道笑話說大了，內部傳真通訊社後來在Twitter留言：「普京有補充：俄羅斯疆域並非無限。」 <br />\n不過，普京這一答引起網民談論，有網民問：「到底普京指的無限，是文化疆域還是俄S400地對空導彈的部署地點？」 <br />\n鑑於俄羅斯2014年吞併克里米亞半島，去年又被格魯吉亞指「悄悄」蠶食其領土，普京這個笑話的確有點敏感。 <br />\n法新社 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161125/55962744\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161125%2F55962744&d=mrgUYd5Ed7UwA6vG9LKaBcW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=7778515d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20161125%2F55962744&h=3ab6d5f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20161125/55962744</a>"},{"pid":"62b3588d50191717f5282f1ddcc9221a90c43e9e","tid":6875,"uid":16110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T14:51:14.000Z","msg":"快點強上蝗國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa30c808278563fd3470e91ea97a93fc51f01d74","tid":6875,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-